ucsessfully complete this objective and an assignment of duties; i.e. - the specific jobs that must be done by our invading forces to retake our relics and those of the opposing realms.<br><br>=============================================<br><br>The lines are drawn, folks. If your guild is all about phat lewts and PvE, we wish you well and good luck in those drops. However, if your guild has EVER expressed a desire to participate in the Relic warfare aspect of this game, we want you. If you want a voice in the future of Relic warfare in Albion on the Palomides server, make sure your guild is represented in the afforementioned chatgroup. So that I and others know this message has been received and accepted, please post in this thread your guild and the member who will be attending, as well as your representative's position in your guild.<br><br>We are entering a new phase in Albion - don't allow yourselves to be left out through inaction.<br><br>Best Regards,<br><br>Keltoth Deathbane <br>Cleric, Church of Albion <br>Aeonian Prophecy <br>============================================<br><br>Only a portion of a pretty cool message..... <br><br>I'm impressed with AP.... Ipno looks like he is making an impact on the guild.  Looks like this has the potential to being a turning point for the realm.<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/fpalomidesfrm8.showMessage?topicID=971.topic">pub15.ezboard.com/fpalomidesfrm8.showMessage?topicID=971.topic</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/usareshft.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saresh FT</A> at: 4/2/02 7:24:32 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ukrystl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krystl</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Duchess</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(4/2